**Color:** Dark backgrounds (#0a0a0f or #1a1410 warm black), gold/champagne accent (#c8a97e or #d4af37), very high contrast text (#f5f0eb warm white).

**Avoid:** Bold sans-serifs (Bebas Neue, Outfit 800), bright colors, rounded fonts. These feel casual, not premium.

Food apps need to stimulate appetite while being functional. Warm colors work — cool blues suppress appetite (literally — that's why diet plates are blue).

**Recommended palette:**
