```
Rule: over 100 lines = too much. Split by responsibility.

Extract shared base + variants:
```css
.btn { padding:12px 24px; border-radius:8px; font:inherit; font-weight:600; cursor:pointer; transition:all 0.2s; }
.btn-primary { background:var(--primary); color:#fff; border:none; }
